   "source": [
    "# In Example 11.4, for what values of $a$ and $b$ do we obtain an absorbing Markov chain?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "_____\n",
    "\n",
    "# $P=\\begin{pmatrix}(1-a) & a\\\\ b & (1-b)\\end{pmatrix}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# This means that we need one of the following conditions to be true:\n",
    "\n",
    "## 1. $(1-a) = 1 \\implies a = 0$\n",
    "\n",
    "## 2. $(1-b) = 0 \\implies b = 0$\n"
   ]
  }
